# - HomeHarbor relabels the live Archiso overlay root after policy load and
#   before PID 1 transitions into init_t.
# - This recipe builds from source; no archlinuxhardened binary package is used.

# ➡️ Pushing pre-releases to [core-testing] can cause havoc, especially
